name: Tooth Protection
text: Our commitment is to provide free and quality ongoing support to all members of our community with our patients well-being in the forefront of our mind. We have a dedicated team of professional practitioners and staff ready to provide ongoing support for all your health care needs.

name: Heart Information and Checkup
text: We have established services woven in preventative care to keep you healthy now and in the future. Our mission is to provide services to all at affordable prices while not sacrificing the quality of services or equipment we use. We bulk bill ALL concession card holders.

name: Caries Defense
text: Our practice is committed to preventative care. We may issue you with a reminder notice from time to time offering you preventative health services appropriate to your care. If you do not wish to be a part of this system please let your doctor or receptionist know.
